  "text": "Clearly, quotient algebra L/I is a Lie algebra, called the corresponding Lie algebra of L. The map I ×L/I → I, (i, x) → [i, x] endows I with a structure of L/I-module (see [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] ).",
